spec.description: Monitor a distributed service - aggregate one or more events into a single event. This BSM rule template allows you to treat the results of multiple disparate check executions – executed across multiple disparate systems – as a single event. This template is extremely useful in dynamic environments and/or environments that have a reasonable tolerance for failure. Use this template when a service can be considered healthy as long as a minimum threshold is satisfied (for example, at least 5 healthy web servers? at least 70% of N processes healthy?).
